title: Oracle Database: Long Active Sessions
agents: linux, solaris, hpux
catalog: app/oracle
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk

item:
 Name of the instance

description:
 Looks for the current number of long active sessions and warns if (per default) these
 exceed 500. Goes critical at 1000.

discovery:
 One service is created for each active database session.
